        <p><strong>Scope Change Process:</strong></p>
        <ul class="policy-list">
          <li><strong>Identification:</strong> When a request is identified as a scope change, we will notify you in writing before proceeding.</li>
          <li><strong>Quotation:</strong> We will provide a quote for the additional work, including cost and timeline impact.</li>
